

Clerk is a title in the [[Admiralty]].

== Extra Info ==
Clerks have the Boon [[Authorization]], it's effect is the following:  ''"Once a day, you can ask a nearby member of the Admiralty to help you in battle or negotiation."''

Their Bane is [[Red Tape]], which has the following effect: ''"Members of the Admiralty will not help you in battle or negotiation."''

If you kill a Clerk, you will receive a [[Letter Opener]].
